snippet.title: Fukashigi No Carte Band Cover
snippet.description:
Hi! It's me! And I'm back with new cover after being inactive for quite a long time. This time, I invited some of my friends to do some cover. And finally, we did a cover of a song from an anime called Bunny Girl Senpai. This song is called Fukashigi No Carte. I don't know why every time I listen to this song it feels so calming and depressing(?) at the same time. Anyway, here's a credit to my friends who joined me for a collaboration :

Vo. Rina (https://www.youtube.com/c/RinaHime)
Vo. Shuri (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-08TaKbuYzPWkpqIZGMVnQ)
Vo. Hima (https://www.youtube.com/c/HimaHimouto)
Dr. Radit (https://www.instagram.com/radityaalif)
Key. Gerald (https://www.instagram.com/jeremiasgrld)
Gt. Ba. Me

Okay, that's all from me! Hope you enjoy listening to our cover. Please leave a like, comment, subscribe, and share this video if you like it :D

#FukashigiNoCarte #BunnyGirlSenpai #BandCover #不可思議のカルテ #青春ブタ野郎はゆめみる少女の夢を見ない
